=== 其他多面體 ===
==== 三角化截角四面體 ====
[[File:Triakis_truncated_tetrahedron.gif|thumb]]
三角化截角四面體為截角四面體進行三角化變換的結果，即將截角四面體的三角形面加入[[三角錐|三角錐]]。

另外一種則是在[[六邊形|六邊形]]面加入[[六角錐|六角錐]]。
== 截角四面體圖 ==
{{Infobox graph
 | name = 截角四面體圖
 | image = [[File:Tuncated_tetrahedral_graph.png|240px]]
 | image_caption = 3倍對稱
 | namesake = 
 | vertices = 12<ref name=ag>An Atlas of Graphs, page=172, C105</ref>
 | edges = 18 
 | automorphisms = 24 ([[Symmetric_group|S<sub>4</sub>]])<ref name=ag/>
 | radius = 3
 | diameter = 3<ref name=ag/>
 | girth = 3<ref name=ag/>
 | chromatic_number = 3<ref name=ag/>
 | chromatic_index = 3<ref name=ag/>
 | fractional_chromatic_index = 
 | properties = [[Hamiltonian_graph|Hamiltonian]], [[regular_graph|regular]], [[K-vertex-connected_graph|3-vertex-connected]], [[planar_graph|planar graph]]
}}
在圖論的數學領域中，與截角四面體相關的圖為'''截角四面體圖'''，其與截角四面體有相同的拓樸結構，是一種{{link-en|阿基米德圖|Archimedean graph}}<ref>{{citation|last1=Read|first1=R. C.|last2=Wilson|first2=R. J.|title=An Atlas of Graphs|publisher=Oxford University Press|year= 1998}}</ref><ref>{{mathworld | urlname = TruncatedTetrahedralGraph | title = Truncated tetrahedral graph}}</ref>，其頂點與邊的數量及結構都與[[阿基米德立體|阿基米德立體]]中的截角四面體相同，具有12個頂點和18個邊<ref>An Atlas of Graphs, page=267, truncated tetrahedral graph</ref>。屬於連結立體圖（{{lang-en|connected cubic graph}}）<ref>An Atlas of Graphs, page=130, connected cubic graphs, 12 vertices, C105</ref>，也是一種連結立體可遞的圖<ref>An Atlas of Graphs, page=161, connected cubic transitive graphs, 12 vertices, Ct11</ref>。
